Why this license
----------------

This repository was prepared as a submission to the Kaggle Gemma 4
Good Hackathon, whose competition rules require winning submissions
to be licensed under CC BY 4.0. The same licence applies to the rest
of the repository so attribution requirements are uniform across the
project.

Once the workflow engine and the visual editor are extracted into
standalone OSS packages (see ``docs/ARCHITECTURE.md`` → Roadmap),
those packages may be relicensed under Apache 2.0 to better fit
developer-library expectations. This repository as a whole will
retain CC BY 4.0 for its content, narrative, and seed data.
